title: Irix ProDev Workshop 5/99
description:
Irix Workshop debugger suite (cvd, cvbuild, cvperf, cvstatic, and dbx.) Includes license. This is pretty dated, so it will complain if you are on something newer that a R10000 (unknown processor type warning which you can ignore.) You may have trouble debugging stuff that is not compiled -o32. 

I'd really, really, really, like to find a newer version of this. Anyone?
